 - use defined MLE_END_DEVICE_TIMEOUT(240s) as child's timeout period;
 - all 4 keep-alive attempts completed in MLE_END_DEVICE_TIMEOUT;

as required in Chapter 4.7.5.

@jwhui , please have a review.
